.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# generated gate output / caches from clean-code-gates runs
**/.cleancode/
**/.dart_mutant_cache
**/mutation-reports/

# local symlink backups created by sync.sh
*.bak-*

# pr-review-report: reviewer-local triage state — untracked by contract
# (references/review-state-schema.md §Provenance & trust: a tracked state file is
# untrusted, forcing a manual override on every review). Shareable history lives in
# the report artifacts under docs/reviews/, not here. Only .pr-review/memory.md is
# meant to be tracked.
/.pr-review/review-state.json

# Generated, non-shipped build artifacts (e.g. inlined explain-codebase demo, bug-6)
/build/

# Generated PR-review HTML reports: regenerated per run and they recursively embed prior
# reports in files[] (arch-4), so they must not live in the reviewed diff / grow unbounded.
# The committed _sample-report.html fixture (used by scripts/validate-pr-review-skill.sh) stays.
/docs/reviews/*.html
!/docs/reviews/_sample-report.html
